<div class="text-3xl pt-8">Elements of the system</div>
<div class="text-xl pt-4 font-extralight">
    <strong>Fundamentals</strong><br/>Within Mística, the <a href="https://brandfactory.telefonica.com/d/iSp7b1DkYygv/n-a#/fundamentals/design-values">basics elements</a> are defined as those commons to the entire system that allow us create components. In this category we include elements such as color constants, fonts, spaces or type of shadows, among others.
</div>
