    <strong>Components</strong><br/>We defined the <a href="https://brandfactory.telefonica.com/d/iSp7b1DkYygv/n-a#/components/overview">components</a> as those elements that have own entity and may o may not be composed of the other more basic elements. These components are used to create the different parts of a screen.
